<MELItem itemNbr="28-25-02" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-28-25-02.1.2-28-25-02">
<Title>APU Fuel Shutoff Valve</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="1" nbrRequired="0" maintIndicator="(M)" opsIndicator="(O)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>May be inoperative provided:</Para>
<List listType="a.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Valve is locked closed.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Left AGCU operates normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>VFSG systems operate normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>EDTO beyond 180 minutes is not conducted.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Note>
<Para>A VFSG system is considered to be operating normally if its associated status message (ELEC GEN SYS L1, L2, R1 or R2) is not displayed.  </Para>
</Note>
<Para>Lock the APU fuel shutoff valve closed (AMM DDG 28-25-02).</Para>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Using a flight deck multi-function display only, open the following circuit breakers and lock with an INOP tag:</Para>
<List listType="A.">
<ListItem>
<Para>APU SOV CLOSE</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>APU SOV OPEN</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Open and deactivate the landing gear doors.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Gain access to the APU fuel shutoff valve actuator in the main wheel well.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Disconnect, cap and stow the valve electrical connector.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Lock the valve closed.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Close the landing gear doors.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
<OperationProcedure>
<List listType="1.">
<ListItem>
<Para>EDTO beyond 180 minutes is not conducted.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Start the first engine using the Ground Power Engine Start Supplementary Procedure.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</OperationProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
